# 📋 APRONIX AI - Complete Setup Guide

## ⚡ Quick Start (5 minutes)

### Step 1: Get Files
Download all 8 files and place them in the same folder:
- index.html
- image.html  
- about.html
- style.css
- app.js
- image.js
- logo.png
- ai-head.png

### Step 2: Get API Key
1. Go to [Google AI Studio](https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey)
2. Click "Create API key in new project"
3. Copy the API key

### Step 3: Open App
1. Open `index.html` in your browser
2. Click Settings (⚙️) button
3. Paste API key
4. Click Save

✅ **Done! You're ready to chat!**

