## 🎯 Detailed Setup Instructions

### Getting Your Gemini API Key

#### Method 1: Using Google AI Studio (Easiest)
1. Visit [Google AI Studio](https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey)
2. Sign in with your Google account
3. Click "Create API key"
4. Select "Create API key in new project"
5. Your API key is generated instantly
6. Copy it with the copy button

#### Method 2: Using Google Cloud Console
1. Go to [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com)
2. Create a new project
3. Enable "Generative Language API"
4. Go to Credentials
5. Create an API key
6. Restrict it to Generative Language API (optional)

### Important Notes About API Keys
- ✅ Free to create
- ✅ No credit card required
- ✅ Rate limits apply (default: 60 requests/minute)
- ⚠️ Keep it private - don't share with anyone
- ⚠️ Delete if compromised

