## 🔐 Privacy & Security

### What APRONIX AI Does
✅ Stores data locally in your browser
✅ Sends prompts only to Google's servers
✅ Uses secure HTTPS connections
✅ Never creates user accounts

### What APRONIX AI Does NOT Do
❌ Track you
❌ Sell your data
❌ Show ads
❌ Require login
❌ Access files on your computer

### Your Data
- All conversations are stored locally
- Only you can access them
- Cleared if you clear browser cache
- Not backed up (backup manually if needed)

